Package: ADVHEIDEL
Type: Package
Title: Advanced Heidelberger-Welch Method
Version: 1.7.0
Author: Soonsung Bae
Maintainer: Soonsung Bae <purun90@gmail.com>
Description: This package performs an advanced Heidelberger-Welch MCMC diagnostic on one or more chains
    with options for different stationarity tests. It includes the Kolmogorov-Smirnov (KS), Cramer-von Mises (CVM),
    Shapiro-Wilk tests, and custom metrics when applicable. The function also calculates the Half-Width ratio for each chain.
